name: Roto-Rooter Plumbers

overview: Roto-Rooter Plumbers of Huntsville and Madison County was established in 1963 and has been family owned since that time. Roto-Rooter Plumbers is customer oriented, delivering quality same day service, with most calls scheduled within two hours. The current owners, David and Deborra Byrd, understand the value of commitment to their community comes from honest relationships and hard work. Roto-Rooter Plumbers strives to deliver the best service at the best value.
